        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="二分查找应用"><a href="#二分查找应用" class="headerlink" title="二分查找应用"></a>二分查找应用</h1><h2 id="实现"><a href="#实现" class="headerlink" title="实现"></a>实现</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\lintao\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\1665321321557.png" alt="1665321321557"></p><pre class=" language-c++"><code class="language-c++">int BinarySearch(int a[], int size, int p)&#123;    int L = 0; //查找区间左端点    int R = size-1; //查找区间右端点    while (L <= R)    &#123;        int mid = L + (R-L) / 2;//正中元素的下标，总个数偶数时是第一个        if (p == a[mid])        &#123;            return mid;        &#125;        else if (p > mid)        &#123;            L = mid + 1;//设置新左端点        &#125;        else            R = mid - 1;//设置新右端点    &#125;    return -1; //返回不存在的下标&#125;//复杂度是log(n)</code></pre><p><img src="C:\Users\lintao\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\1665323654831.png" alt="1665323654831"></p><pre class=" language-c++"><code class="language-c++">int LowerBound(int a[],int size, int p)&#123;    int L = 0;    int R = size - 1;    int lastPos = -1;//最近一次更新    while (L <= R)    &#123;        int mid = L + (L-R) / 2;        if (a[mid] >= p)        &#123;            R = mid - 1;        &#125;        else        &#123;            lastPos = mid;            L = mid + 1;        &#125;    &#125;    return lastPos;&#125;</code></pre><p>注意：数组里必须是排好序的元素</p><p><img src="C:\Users\lintao\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\1665324365222.png" alt="1665324365222"></p>]]></content>
      
      
